    public class SongCollectionTableModel
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.swing.table.TableModel, javax.swing.ListModel
    Author:
    Brian Wehrle, Patrick Maley Class Description: SongCollectionTableModel adapts our SongCollection class to be displayed as a TableModel object. It provides all the necessary methods to implement TableModel.
